Brian Nicol dived into a pool at a luxury holiday villa in the Costa del Sol but failed to resurface . 
  The 32-year-old from Glasgow was staying with friends in Nueva Andalucia . 
  He had been on a night out in Marbella before arriving in the area on Saturday . 
  Paramedics tried to save him but he died in the pool on Easter Sunday . 
  Police said early evidence suggests his death was a tragic accident . 
 